                     <interp inst="t18230219-97-person915" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live opposite the prosecutor's. I saw the prisoner unpin the handkerchief. The witness stopped him.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I heard an alarm; a man threw the handkerchief down, and I picked it up and put it in my bosom.</p>
